    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/4eb43472206390049fc39b8ac450e4ad.avif?t=1756263981\" width=616 height=130 /></span> <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/56411fc61b9f1a903a1eab7fa3f405b7.poster.avif?t=1756263981\" width=800 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/56411fc61b9f1a903a1eab7fa3f405b7.webm?t=1756263981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/56411fc61b9f1a903a1eab7fa3f405b7.mp4?t=1756263981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/894812133f77a7fba479d411a66c77e8.avif?t=1756263981\" width=616 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WyshBound is an action-adventure RPG across a realm of eccentric kingdoms. Meet companions equipped with unique abilities, solve challenging puzzles, and collect powerful flowers to defeat the villainous Fangor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/b1ad13a5b0d7154bf3be93aaf3aede7a.avif?t=1756263981\" width=616 height=94 /></span>In WyshBound, companions are key. Each member of your party has a unique set of abilities, which you'll need to surpass obstacles, defeat enemies, and solve puzzles!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/b65af8ffc8071355f2e097a18dfff9ec.poster.avif?t=1756263981\" width=800 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/b65af8ffc8071355f2e097a18dfff9ec.webm?t=1756263981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/b65af8ffc8071355f2e097a18dfff9ec.mp4?t=1756263981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Companions are found throughout the game, so there's always a new friend to meet and a new ability to master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/3a631eb5a741108d7f98244e3a860bf3.poster.avif?t=1756263981\" width=800 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/3a631eb5a741108d7f98244e3a860bf3.webm?t=1756263981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/3a631eb5a741108d7f98244e3a860bf3.mp4?t=1756263981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/a090b09ca9c5892172945d82b48ff13e.avif?t=1756263981\" width=616 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >WyshBound is no simple stroll from room to room. Puzzles are interspersed across the world, calling back to the nostalgic design of classic action-adventure games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/8d74b62ee580f6cf71f10eef95bfa545.poster.avif?t=1756263981\" width=800 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/8d74b62ee580f6cf71f10eef95bfa545.webm?t=1756263981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/8d74b62ee580f6cf71f10eef95bfa545.mp4?t=1756263981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/bb65d3dabb42592ab446e6e9cfc817f0.avif?t=1756263981\" width=616 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each character is personally crafted and drawn frame-by-frame, giving them all a unique personality. Just look at that mustache bounce!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/c4693ff7fa13b78f6d41fa6b74c75587.poster.avif?t=1756263981\" width=800 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/c4693ff7fa13b78f6d41fa6b74c75587.webm?t=1756263981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/c4693ff7fa13b78f6d41fa6b74c75587.mp4?t=1756263981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/b3e50b1c68ffc081418fc58c1713818a.avif?t=1756263981\" width=616 height=94 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each enemy type is designed to stand out with a personal moveset, making every encounter different from the last!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/d613975944f836e98614b9f01dcdadb8.poster.avif?t=1756263981\" width=800 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/d613975944f836e98614b9f01dcdadb8.webm?t=1756263981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/d613975944f836e98614b9f01dcdadb8.mp4?t=1756263981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/c144488ca9d2bf42fff45b29ce72610e.poster.avif?t=1756263981\" width=800 height=490 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/c144488ca9d2bf42fff45b29ce72610e.webm?t=1756263981\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3171520/extras/c144488ca9d2bf42fff45b29ce72610e.mp4?t=1756263981\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >If you've read this far, why not try the game out for yourself? Our demo covers a portion of our first chapter, where you will meet your companions Eva and Pandora, and maybe a few hostile vegetables along the way!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
